\"xx-large\"><strong><em><span class=\"red\">唔洗再同班人互屌喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冷處理is ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n謙係有做得唔好嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔完美，需改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n不過你問我佢藍定黃嘅話，<br />\n我諗係chill club嘅拉票時間，<br />\n佢唱最後信仰都冇唱一人之境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過佢對個獎，<br />\n我唔知佢係唔知要攞定點？<br />\n佢攞第二，三個獎嗰時又攞又放，<br />\n似係唔知點做多啲？<br />\n<br />\n加上，<br />\n酒精會蝕食唔同物質其實係一直都有嘅mind set嚟<br />\n呢個我覺得佢嘅擔心係make sense喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過話個event求其就真係差！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知係講笑失咗分寸定點喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔得體！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過TVB嘅頒獎禮，<br />\n我覺得場地氣氛都同今日唔同，<br />\n平時上chill club應該成日同牙科9up，<br />\n先咁chill 啫？（估咋）<br />\n不過最後件事點都係要係謙點做，<br />\n所以唔好jer 嘅粉絲喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當互相尊重喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n希望大家可以欣賞下香港樂壇喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 有投Jer<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><em><span class=\"red\">做得唔好睇係事實<br />\n而我地都唔應該再推高件事<br />\n由得謙自己搞喇<br />\n唔好幫倒幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></em></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1c25af10fc7f69d06a6fe5284439170aeff90109","tid":2495804,"uid":345195,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b30d1944922eda59514646e6ceae17d04687659","tid":2495804,"uid":230590,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8d32c2e4e09e5187fae65ad3c8505ac85c1655dc","tid":2495804,"uid":345195,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"347934b974d5ea2636fa26e2a495c4c0fdfeec05","tid":2495804,"uid":257781,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:49:35.000Z","msg":"酒精對木、金屬都會造成磨損 你隻手掂得多酒精都會乾 <br />\n不過點諗都唔會係怕揦仲用手去掂啦 真係唔知邊個兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽過幾首歌都叫fans既話 咁咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"酒精會揦有乜咁出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心唔明屌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:18:57.000Z","msg":"揦到個獎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"門把都會揦到㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小心啲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mobile01.com/topicdetail.php?f=356&amp;t=5570361\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mobile01.com%2Ftopicdetail.php%3Ff%3D356%26t%3D5570361&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx2WzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=d98aaf8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mobile01.com/topicdetail.php?f=356&amp;t=5570361</a>"},{"pid":"8c24560adf354229c9df2f306f00df15926dee6